Silly hellian.  Dragons don't use tools.  Those are for nakas.  Claws is all you need.  Just go to your abilities menu, select the tradeskill part of it (other is combat, don't recall the exact names), and drag the appropriate skills up to your hotkey bar.  Click to use.
